/>\n我諗我基本對話 應該無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你要求係乜<br />\n如果只計你講呢三間<br />\n錢一定係KA，crew life一定係CX<br />\n英文呢d冇話咩程度<br />\n當然conversational English is a must<br />\n就算你考試低分都冇問題<br />\n表達到自己唔好甩甩咳咳就得<br />\n所以如果你講唔係特別好<br />\n少講少錯"},{"pid":"8ac3b9c17fe2e9e0350a0f45b79eefd8ff1d8314","tid":162023,"uid":25522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有要求<br />\n陰毛唔可以長過碌能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔要呢個要求呀 最多剃哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nKeep住笑<br />\n頭髮露額<br />\n唔好太多野講<br />\n最好剃手毛(可剃埋陰毛)<br />\n其他都係正常manner</blockquote><br />\n唔好太多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁番邊間好 可以飛多d唔同國家<br />\n見完幾耐會有結果 出結果後幾耐要去training</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果計多國家一定係CX/EK/JL<br />\nKA/UO/HX航線相對少而且多day turn冇乜crew life<br />\n<br />\n2nd in完好快有offer<br />\n通常一batch出offer之後一齊train<br />\n最快offer後兩星期上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂先 咁排次序去in cx &gt; hx &gt;ka咁好無<br />\nCx係咪最難 英文程度要大概幾高<br />\n我諗我基本對話 應該無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你要求係乜<br />\n如果只計你講呢三間<br />\n錢一定係KA，crew life一定係CX<br />\n英文呢d冇話咩程度<br />\n當然conversational English is a must<br />\n就算你考試低分都冇問題<br />\n表達到自己唔好甩甩咳咳就得<br />\n所以如果你講唔係特別好<br />\n少講少錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊apply好 定 一個一個黎好<br />\n小肥得唔得 米8 拉番望落無咁肥<br />\n皮膚唔好 暗瘡好得差唔多 但有d凹凸洞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285cd85a43dff9c5c1c53dc6d8bf63bf034e873c","tid":162023,"uid":6